# 🆓 Free & Low-Cost Cybersecurity Training Matrix

| **Provider's Name** | **Certification / Track** | **Focus Area** | **Time Frame** | **Ideal For / Focus Area** | **Career Roles / Direction (Red / Blue / Purple Hat)** | **Cost (ZAR)** | **Website** | **Deployment Strategy / Recommended Study Materials / Roadmap Positioning or Role** |
|---------------------|---------------------------|----------------|----------------|-----------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------|----------------|-------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| CompTIA             | ITF+ / Security+          | Cybersecurity fundamentals | 30–60 hrs      | Interns, Junior Analysts     | Blue Hat (Security Awareness), Purple Hat (GRC Starter) | ~2,500–7,500   | [comptia.org](https://www.comptia.org/en-us/certifications/) | CertMaster Learn, Professor Messer, foundational for GRC and SOC onboarding |
| Cisco               | CCST Cybersecurity        | Threats, CIA triad         | 15–30 hrs      | Students, Entry-level Tech Roles | Blue Hat (SOC Prep), Purple Hat (Governance Literacy) | Free–Low       | [netacad.com](https://www.netacad.com/) | Cisco NetAcad modules, GitHub Pages integration, ideal for onboarding kits |
| TryHackMe           | Pre-Security / Intro Labs | Hands-on basics            | 20–40 hrs      | Beginners, Career Explorers   | Red Hat (Lab Exposure), Blue Hat (Detection Basics)    | Free–Low       | [tryhackme.com](https://tryhackme.com/welcome) | Gamified labs, badge tracker, sprint planner integration |
| EC-Council          | Essentials Series (NDE, EHE, DFE) | Digital forensics, network, ethical hacking | 30–50 hrs | Entry-level Security Learners | Red Hat (EHE), Blue Hat (NDE), Purple Hat (DFE)        | Free–Low       | [eccouncil.org](https://www.eccouncil.org/) | CodeRed platform, LinkedIn badge-ready, GitHub onboarding module |
| Fortinet            | FCF – Fundamentals        | Threat landscape, basics   | 10–20 hrs      | Onboarding, Non-tech Consultants | Blue Hat (SOC Literacy), Purple Hat (Risk Awareness)   | Free–Low       | [fortinet.com](https://training.fortinet.com/) | Fortinet NSE Institute, governance-aligned starter track |
| Google              | Cybersecurity Certificate | Online safety & fundamentals | ~40 hrs       | Career switchers, SME teams   | Blue Hat (Privacy), Purple Hat (Digital Ethics)        | Free–Low       | [grow.google](https://grow.google/intl/ssa-en/courses-and-tools/) | Career-aligned, governance-ready, ideal for stakeholder literacy |
| FreeCodeCamp        | InfoSec Projects          | Hands-on labs              | Self-paced     | Self-learners, interns        | Red Hat (Lab Practice), Blue Hat (Security Hygiene)    | Free           | [freecodecamp.org](https://www.freecodecamp.org/learn/information-security/) | GitHub integration, project-based learning, sprint planner compatible |

