| ISC²                | CISSP + Concentrations    | Governance, architecture, risk | 100–120 hrs    | Senior Consultants, Risk Officers | Purple Hat (Governance), Blue Hat (Security Management) | ~12,000–20,000 | [isc2.org](https://www.isc2.org/) | CBK domains, Sybex CISSP Guide, ideal for boardroom credibility |
| ISACA               | CISM / CISA               | Audit, risk, governance | 80–100 hrs     | Governance Professionals     | Purple Hat (Audit & Compliance)                        | ~15,000–25,000 | [isaca.org](https://www.isaca.org/) | ISACA study guides, ideal for GRC-aligned consultants |
| GIAC / SANS         | GPEN / GSEC / GCIH        | Pentesting, incident response | 60–100 hrs     | Red/Blue Team Leads          | Red Hat (GPEN), Blue Hat (GCIH), Purple Hat (GSEC)     | ~20,000–35,000 | [giac.org](https://www.giac.org/) | SANS labs, strategic for enterprise security teams |

